==Important Notes==
*If you are having difficulties using this template, [[User_blog:Dragonjet/KC3%E6%94%B9|KC3 Kai]] has a built-in exporter. This allows you to just copy-paste the code and have it working.
*Instead of using this template, you can also just screenshot your fleet and post that. It may prove easier for some.

==Basic==
;Description
:This is a very lightweight template running on Lua.
;Credits
:[[User:Nanamin|Nanamin]]
;Skeleton
<pre>{{EventComp
| <Ship>/<Remodel>
| <Level>
| <Equipment>
| <Equipment>
| <Equipment>
| <Equipment>
|-
| hq = 
}}</pre>

==Syntax==
*''Ship'' is the ship's name. For example, "Sendai".
*''Remodel'' is the ship's remodel. This may be "", "Kai", "Kai Ni", "A", "Carrier", "Carrier Kai", "Carrier Kai Ni", "zwei" or "drei".
*''Level'' is the ship's current level.
*''Equipment'' is the ship's equipment. Slot order does matter as it is used to calculate the ship's fighter power. Names are as listed on the wikia.
;Special Values
:''hq'' is your HQ level.

